      "amount": "1/4 teaspoon"
    },
    {
      "name": "black pepper",
      "amount": "1/4 teaspoon"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the grill to medium-high heat.",
    "Thread the watermelon and honeydew melon cubes onto skewers, leaving a small space between each piece.",
    "Wrap each skewer with a slice of prosciutto.",
    "Brush the skewers with olive oil and season with smoked paprika, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Grill the skewers for 2-3 minutes per side, or until the prosciutto is crispy.",
    "Drizzle the skewers with balsamic vinegar and sprinkle with chopped fresh mint leaves.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy.",
    "Garnish with additional mint leaves and melon slices, if desired."
  ],
